<h3 dir=3D"auto">Bug: Email Label Rollback Fails to Restore Original Stat=
e</h3>


<p dir=3D"auto">The rollback logic for email label modifications in <code=
 class=3D"notranslate">markEmailReadStatusWithRecovery</code> and <code c=
lass=3D"notranslate">toggleEmailStarWithRecovery</code> appears to incorr=
ectly reverse the original operation. When an initial label change (like =
marking as read/unread or starring/unstarring) fails, the subsequent roll=
back attempt uses <code class=3D"notranslate">addLabelIds</code> and <cod=
e class=3D"notranslate">removeLabelIds</code> in a way that does not prop=
erly restore the email's previous state.</p>


